Logical Model: AD: PostalAddress (V3 Data Type)

Official URL: http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/StructureDefinition/AD Version: 2.0.0-sd-202406-matchbox-patch
Active as of 2024-06-19 Computable Name: AD

Mailing and home or office addresses. A sequence of address parts, such as street or post office Box, city, postal code, country, etc.

Usage:

  • Use this Logical Model Profile: AssignedAuthor (CDA Class), AssignedEntity (CDA Class), AssociatedEntity (CDA Class), Criterion (CDA Class)... Show 12 more, CustodianOrganization (CDA Class), Guardian (CDA Class), IntendedRecipient (CDA Class), LabCriterion (CDA Class), Observation (CDA Class), ObservationRange (CDA Class), Organization (CDA Class), ParticipantRole (CDA Class), PatientRole (CDA Class), Place (CDA Class), RelatedEntity (CDA Class) and RelatedSubject (CDA Class)
